data.description: This is it, your new home in beautiful Alpharetta! This home offers a seamless blend of style and functionality with its open concept design. The kitchen and living room flow effortlessly, creating an ideal space for both daily living and entertaining. The breakfast bar adds a touch of convenience, perfect for casual dining or socializing. Equipped with mixed appliances, the kitchen boasts modern functionality while maintaining a sleek aesthetic. Natural light floods the living area, enhancing the inviting atmosphere. Two bedrooms and a well-appointed bathroom provide comfort and privacy. Beyond the comforts of your home you have access to a sparkling pool and tennis courts. This condo boasts a strategic location just minutes away from downtown Alpharetta, Halcyon, and Avalon. Explore the vibrant downtown area with its charming shops, diverse dining options, and cultural attractions. Halcyon and Avalon offer a modern twist to shopping and entertainment, ensuring you have a variety of experiences at your doorstep.
